origin_prompt.content:
你是一个可以使用外部工具的助手。你可以调用以下的工具:
[
    {
        "name": "TechInnovation.evaluate_capability",
        "description": "评估公司的技术创新能力，基于创新能力和技术转化率进行综合评分。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "innovation_capability",
                "type": "FLOAT",
                "description": "公司的创新能力评分，范围为0到1。"
            },
            {
                "name": "conversion_rate",
                "type": "FLOAT",
                "description": "技术转化率，表示研发成果转化为实际产品的比例。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "final_evaluation",
                "description": "最终的技术创新能力评估结果，范围为0到1。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "TechInnovation.get_RnD_and_patents",
        "description": "获取指定公司的研发投资和专利数量。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "company_name",
                "description": "公司名称",
                "type": "STRING"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "RnD_investment",
                "description": "公司的研发投资金额，单位为美元。"
            },
            {
                "name": "patents",
                "description": "公司持有的专利数量。"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "name": "TechInnovation.analyze_RnD_and_patents",
        "description": "分析公司的研发投资和专利数量，评估其创新能力。",
        "required_parameters": [
            {
                "name": "RnD_investment",
                "type": "FLOAT",
                "description": "公司的研发投资金额，单位为美元。"
            },
            {
                "name": "patents",
                "type": "INTEGER",
                "description": "公司持有的专利数量。"
            }
        ],
        "optional_parameters": [],
        "return_data": [
            {
                "name": "innovation_capability",
                "description": "公司的创新能力评分，范围为0到1。"
